					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"602cd7a5-fb18-48df-af4e-6cec6fcd6fb4\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"binding-strike\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Binding Strike</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"07064695-8e6d-4f26-93a5-58c46b793c22\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Special Activation\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Special Activation\">★</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"19e7c287-48d7-468f-8c09-13386533e7e5\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You “paint” your ammunition with Adhesion before throwing or firing it at a target, transferring the infusion to one of your target’s possessions.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"8c570800-96d5-4bbc-a73b-21946d9b0e43\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">You can use Binding Strike when you hit with a <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"ranged-attacks\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">ranged attack</tooltip> at any distance, and you don’t need to touch the infused targets or have a hand free.</p>",
